{"tid":2000202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★香港殯儀館冧假天花 法事繼續舉行","createTime":"2020-05-03T16:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T12:39:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f818eb733b9021eab719f8db2698b5a18c32cac4","tid":2000202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"（3日）早上時分，北角香港殯儀館大堂一幅假天花被發現倒塌。據網民圖片所見，現場地面滿佈瓦礫，假天花上鐵支有鐵鏽痕迹。另外翻查資料圖片，倒塌假天花位置有一盞巨型吊燈，相信也在事故中損毀。<br />\n<br />\n不過，現場所見地下兩個靈堂其中一間仍有法事舉行，相信殯儀館運作不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200503/7KPWBVQ4NFNQJGFMCEPUB2Y3RU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200503%2F7KPWBVQ4NFNQJGFMCEPUB2Y3RU%2F&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=dc615433\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200503%2F7KPWBVQ4NFNQJGFMCEPUB2Y3RU%2F&h=7ad4c436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200503/7KPWBVQ4NFNQJGFMCEPUB2Y3RU/</a>"},{"pid":"6f01f1de647db0a69b5c39b5832127af669c48e9","tid":2000202,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n顯靈"},{"pid":"61ab2e361e6fc2e52bc9a37a108a4929f6b53b85","tid":2000202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"48c55395831d8675264ea51b86e0864f4d2eb49d","tid":2000202,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61ab2e361e6fc2e52bc9a37a108a4929f6b53b85","tid":2000202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"真係二世"}]}